{"tid":1569934,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［野餐頻道，證實係鬼，請廣傳］","createTime":"2019-09-14T20:37:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-15T05:26:26.000Z","uid":173858,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"dd4017c5fd191908ac3b5a442b14a2802fab02eb","tid":1569934,"uid":173858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T20:37:21.000Z","msg":"［野餐頻道，證實係鬼，請廣傳］［退group保平安］<br />\n@hkpicnic 一定係鬼group！<br />\n平時冇乜野，關鍵時刻就出招。<br />\n第一：914叫人去淘大，搞到手足被人打到重傷、然後被捕。<br />\n第二：想搞散915大遊行，居然叫人唔好去銅鑼灣，反而去apm商場。<br />\n手足小心，入左即刻 leave group。<br />\n佢係黑警/藍屍開既，fact checked。<br />\n（野餐頻道admin請關閉群組，唔好再藍屍扮黃絲害死我地手足）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/09/15/043609_99a8c9feb32d259f25626b40cc593308.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F09%2F15%2F043609_99a8c9feb32d259f25626b40cc593308.png&h=e42522bb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/09/15/043611_ad210f193f9807ae763f0b724d2165a3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F09%2F15%2F043611_ad210f193f9807ae763f0b724d2165a3.png&h=5dfb97c8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0896933011ab510226a525747825b79156bf72c8","tid":1569934,"uid":95588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T22:40:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0baf341426ed6777c8d7bad2aca0400581b9614b","tid":1569934,"uid":224657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T04:08:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3a046b555fa5026f53e69d4ff4e10eb07066bf3f","tid":1569934,"uid":301989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s